Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪谈 柳树老人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简易式如下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What an honest boy you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是诚实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要成为命令句就会成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be an honest this boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为诚实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的课到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些时间 我们来谈谈别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么谈些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猥谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你刚才说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚实的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 像这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…怪谈 怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定权在我！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪谈到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪谈便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我友引高中也有外人所不知 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛骨悚然的七大怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里在建校前是墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不在的钢琴室传出钢琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用之后会不明原因死亡的禁开之铁柜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其四！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会笑的骷髅标本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其五！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了樱花花季时节  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会造成集团打瞌睡的恐怖落榜教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其六！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人红斗篷的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其七！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会笑的镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么没了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得您好像要讲怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种传说 每一所学校都有那么一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的什么玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会那就是怪谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那时怪谈 被传开会哭死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是严正地开始陈述的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能用这到处骗小孩的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么结束呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面所说的话 是要进入主题的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说是气氛的制造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊 也就是说序曲了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会做 不是每个人都能做到的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！真是不好搞的一群小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该进入主题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快…快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然先前的全是刺探 正题在这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概这个故事 谁也没有听过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个 就用这个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校园的一角有一株老柳树儜立在那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前有个学生 在那柳树树干上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位这是卓利根的刀子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的是刀的锋利度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这锋利度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是德国制造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤到柳树的学生 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发了40度高烧倒在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地狱般的痛苦缠斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年后的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这世间离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要吓我啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在那过世的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说柳树会发光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言那个光 可能是那学生所插的刀子 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被月光所反射造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把它忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 达令 我想看那棵柳树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个故事是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棵柳树吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是假的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是温泉在痛苦挣扎中制造的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概也是如此 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你该不会信那话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刀子也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对卓利根这个名牌就有点真实性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦 梦！是温泉的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概领了退休金就马上想买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细看看 刀子的痕迹一点也没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是编出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 近来的教师都想受到学生的重视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂个鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可以见到诅咒者咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真相信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种傻子听的怪谈故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 你看看这快倒掉的枯木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连诅咒的气力也全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在别人身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还相信有诅咒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过真实了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所诅咒的学生是坏学生不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老伯伯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是哪位 真谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为谢礼 给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏的藏处！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我详细看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我看着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些只有欲望没有道德感的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要给你们一个报应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年轻人连小孩也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我有什么仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么 嘴给我放尊重点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这老头打了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对年长者 你那口气算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不服气 那就在今晚十二点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至友引高中钟楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！你到要愚弄我面堂终太郎至什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果挖到宝 我们从明天就是大富豪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也有我一份咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 我们三人对分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看！面堂追不上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不管了面堂如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜 今晚十二点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老人只是用步走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的面堂居然追不上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 逃跑速度真快的老头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记着 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想决胜负的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今晚十二点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请个警卫嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今老师代替警卫的学校还真没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不在的音乐教室中 传出点点钢琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吓我可没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那么老套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星那小子 想这种傻把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不轻饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩够了没！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音大雨点小 只有猫一只
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了樱花季节 会造成集体瞌睡的落榜教室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了没有 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用者会不明因素死亡 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁开的铁柜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有宝藏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着 十二点整挖钟楼之影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你躲着 诸星！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要玩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不生气了 快出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 学生是那样 老师也半斤八两
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对古老的东西 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人生的先圣尊敬之心一点也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都腐败了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想静静的安眠 但被吵醒的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这承袭中国四千年妖怪的流动之柳树精
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些腐败之人心再加以打醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这时来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 你又来做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是值夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要在十二点 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在钟楼前和侮辱我的老人决斗而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 这和他无关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要阻挠我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在决斗时间迟到 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会将耻辱带至面堂后代 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们尝尝我柳精王的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是想挖宝的小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么挖宝藏都未发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样把他们活埋了 那另一个则…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子可能会武装而来 所以从后面这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他倒挂当晒鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样正正当当地给予诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 够了没！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 请放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉符号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你们在此时此地出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这啊 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 面堂 说谎马上就被拆穿了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星和我无关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间快到了 请顾及武士的颜面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在此繁忙之际…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 喂 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去哪儿？等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是激烈的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这些人话是讲不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来挖宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻子 谁会相信这种鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想骗大人没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗老师也得不到什么利益 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是年龄大了点 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说是大人 还真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好机会 今日好好教训你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用放屁的空气压力推动的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超小型耕耘机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆同学 稍微将声音放小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某大学的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今日一般公开化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个构想者是个女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盲肠手术后 造成经常放气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:29.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梅酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然不听我的教训 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把我当傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 教训能清醒的时候听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清刀柄的清酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你装什么帅嘛 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒不喝做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样清刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷了就太浪费了 你这傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒一滴即米一粒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做会遭天谴之事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我站好 我把你劈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 居然把那凶器带到学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要喝别人的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是由我们那里没收的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么检查物品 居然在此中饱私囊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这欺诈的官员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来制裁你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 谁是幕府官员！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 和你们无法清醒交谈 借来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来的小子连时间都不守了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也有我的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！好暗、好窄、好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会做这种无聊事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外 没有别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 用谈的就能了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 达令的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我连地位也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名誉也 财产也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.26,0:23:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今日起我就不是面堂家的长男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个杀人魔了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你劈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 我是冤枉的
